<section class="section" style="background-color: var(--color-white);">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Evolution: Flat 2.0 / Almost Flat</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--color-success);">
        <h3 class="card-title">Google Material Design</h3>
        <p class="card-content">
          <strong>Year:</strong> 2014<br><br>
          Added subtle depth back to flat design. Shadows show elevation. Motion creates 
          dimension. Called "Flat 2.0" - balances aesthetics with usability.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);">
        <h3 class="card-title">iOS 10-15 Evolution</h3>
        <p class="card-content">
          <strong>Years:</strong> 2016-2021<br><br>
          Apple refined flat design adding subtle depth for usability. Larger buttons, 
          clearer affordances. Still fundamentally flat with refinements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

